    "body": "A better approach - allow comments after a revert or require that give the dev error strings. This would be a far cleaner approach.\r\n\r\ninstead of: ``require(foo | bar, \"dev: no foo bar\");``\r\n\r\nit could be: ``require(foo | bar); // dev: no foo bar``",
